umber of Asset Risks related to them</p>','2023-01-17 19:26:11','2023-01-17 19:26:11'),(26,37,'missing-business-risks-section','BusinessUnits',1,'<h2>Business&nbsp;Units Missing Business Risk Analysis</h2><p>This pie chart shows, for each business unit, the percentage of processes which have no Business Risks associated</p>','2023-01-17 19:26:11','2023-01-17 19:26:11'),(27,38,'missing-risks-section','BusinessUnits',1,'<h2>Business Units Missing Asset Risk Analysis</h2><p>This pie chart shows, for each business unit, the percentage of assets which have no Risks associated</p>','2023-01-17 19:26:11','2023-01-17 19:26:11'),(28,46,'1','ComplianceExceptions',0,'<h2><b>Top Ten Exceptions by Compliance Package</b></h2><p>This pie charts shows the top 10 compliance packages by their number of asociated exceptions.</p>','2023-01-17 19:26:11','2023-01-17 19:26:11'),(29,47,'2','ComplianceExceptions',0,'<h2><b>Exceptions by Duration</b></h2><p>This chart shows exceptions distributed by their duration from start to close date.</p>','2023-01-17 19:26:11','2023-01-17 19:26:11'),(30,50,'3','CompliancePackageRegulators',0,'<h3>Current Compliance Status</h3><p>This chart shows for each chapter what is the current compliance status and the number of compliance requirements that have some sort of issue. This is calculated by looking at the treatment selected for each compliance package and their related statuses</p>','2023-01-17 19:26:11','2023-01-17 19:26:11'),(31,51,'package-requirements-item','CompliancePackageRegulators',0,'<h3>Compliance by Proportion of Requirements</h3><p>This chart shows for every chapter what percentage of the requirements has what type of treatment assigned: policies, projects, internal controls and exceptions.</p>','2023-01-17 19:26:11','2023-01-17 19:26:11'),(32,52,'dashboard-chart','ComplianceManagements',1,'<h3>Items grouped by Status</h3><p>This chart shows for every compliance item the current treatment status. This is achieved by looking at the treatme